events.text: OooOOOwww so close! You almost got fourth place!!
Yah [pn] you did amazing! You rolled just like a [wave amp=100 freq=5]sphere[/wave]!
Thanks, all of you were so fast
[i]Why am I so bad at rolling? All my points hurt. If I had more angles I could roll just like them.[/i]
The spheres start to brag towards each other again.
Feeling disappointed you move away from the circles.
